## Key Insights

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Critical Success Factors:**
> 1. **Speed is paramount** - Every action should feel instant (<200ms for interactions)
> 2. **Clarity over complexity** - Show only essential information, hide advanced features behind "More" options
> 3. **Trust through transparency** - Always show data freshness and loading states

> [!TIP]
> **Quick Wins:**
> - Add skeleton loaders for all async operations
> - Implement keyboard shortcuts for power users (e.g., `Cmd+K` for search)
> - Provide "Tour" or "What's New" tooltip for first-time users

